markdownRemark.html: See F. Lazzari and M. Lozzi, Gli epigrammi di Antonio Mancinelli, Velletri, 2009, 27-31 and passim, who explicate the patrons of Mancinelli, especially at Rome, in some detail, based on a close reading of the epigrams published in 1503.
